headline: Oneok Inc. (OKE) Q1 Earnings Miss Estimates
summary: Oneok (OKE) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -15.45% and 14.89%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
